Product Description

Twinkle Star 300LED Warm White Curtain String Lights create romantic life for you.

600 LED Curtain String Lights 300 LED Curtain String Lights 12 Stars Curtain String Lights 200 LED String Lights Photo Clips String Lights Copper Wire String Lights
LED Quantity 600 300 138 200 20 100
Length 20*9.8ft 6.6*9.8ft 6.7*3.3ft 83ft 10ft 33ft
Color Warm WhIte White Warm White Warm White Warm WhIte Warm WhIte
Power Source Adaptor Operated Adaptor Operated Adaptor Operated Adaptor Operated Battery Operated USB Operated




8 Modes Setting

1.Combination 2.In Waves 3.Sequential  4.Slo-Glo 5.Chasing/Flash 6.Slow Fade 7.Twinkle 8.Steady On

High Brightness

300 WARM WHITE LED lights, widespread lighting source, provide powerful light, and create romantic life for you.

Waterproof

The curtain light is waterproof and designed to withstand light rain or water spills, perfect for outdoor & indoor decoration.

Waterproof level is IP44, but the power and controller is non-waterproof, please keep them away from water.

Read more

Specifications:

Size: 6.6ft×9.8ft

LED Color: WARM WHITE

LED Quantity: 300 LEDs

Waterproof Level: IP44

Voltage: 110V, Output: 29V safe low voltage (Includes UL plug-in transformer)

Plug to the controller: 1ft, Controller to the LED light: 8.9ft

Notes:

White buckle is to fix the main power cord line, can not be cut, otherwise the string lights will be separated!

5.0 out of 5 starsBeautiful
January 8, 2019
Verified Purchase
I purchased one order of these lights to hang in my livingroom window for some gentle, ambiant light. I had the sheer curtains already there looking out onto our backyard. There are several different settings for the lights (still, blinking, fade... etc). These are just the right length for a window about 2 doorways wide. I was worried that the lights might heat up causing a fire hazard being next to the sheer curtains but the lights themselves do not get hot, or even warm. There are 10 strings hanging off of the main string which are quite long. The plug in cord is long enough that it can reach the floor from up near the ceiling,a nd then some. I will most likely be buying another set in the near future.
